description: uSync, database to and from file syncronisation for umbraco. For umbraco v7.1+
releaseNotes:
v2.4.12 
Moved the dashboard files to App_Plugins to make upgrading nicer, and prep for 7.3 (no more spreadsheets)

v2.4.11
- better nuget Package, doesn't kill the dashboard section on upgrade/removal

v2.4.10 
-Importing new templates doesn't overwrite template source files on disk.
- Tracker doesn't use Hash value from config files anymore.

v2.4.9 
- Improvements in change tracking
better support for composite datatypes

v.2.4.7
- Better checking for missing datatypes (no YSOD when packages haven't been installed)
- Changing the base type of datatypes (experimental)

2.4.5
- better support for preValues in datatypes

2.4.3 
- support to stop uSync folder being created at all (attach=false, write=false)

v2.4 
- Major update to many elements of sync code
- lots of better matching for imports of doctype properties, and less double saving of things that haven't changed.
title: uSync for Umbraco
